{"tid":11412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"放底你最想同呀爸/呀媽講咩？","createTime":"2016-11-29T09:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T12:19:57.000Z","uid":23909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03710816be34f399720380475d73f178eaed94d7","tid":11412,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:35:15.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到你兩個冇再成日家嘈屋閉我地成家都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由細到大我成績唔上唔落 你地都對我冇乜要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由我自己鍾意做乜就做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都幾多謝你地冇將我變成一個書蟲<br />\n多謝老母你唔會將我拍拖件事同我老豆講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你地暫時都未離開我身邊 我會珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果要講唔好嘅野，就係成日叫我唔好上LIHKG(之前係高登)"},{"pid":"5fe4c5c072babf778ade169ab4660aa60deb85e5","tid":11412,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:35:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3dc2b46240a38e8ea24b880cfe77f66e7290ae83","tid":11412,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:36:03.000Z","msg":"一家之主唔係大撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dea7b9a9d076d3c7e13bdb762e6f2b20e5ee3af","tid":11412,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd627fe6f665f3488de7a6bf8a5fe2d99dad3a06","tid":11412,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a978111ea5afe65bf7130939fe98a2f5ba99b0","tid":11412,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re